<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أشفق منهما <span class="c2">(أصحاب)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> محمد <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">(وكانت)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> تسمى <span class="c2">(الفاضحة)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
